org.apache.axis.wsdl.fromJava
Class FieldRep

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.apache.axis.wsdl.fromJava.BaseRep
        |
        +--org.apache.axis.wsdl.fromJava.FieldRep
public class FieldRep
extends BaseRep

FieldRep is the representation of a class used inside the Java2WSDL emitter. The information in the FieldRep can be changed by user provided code to affect the emitted wsdl file. (See ClassRep)

Author:
Rich Scheuerle (scheu@us.ibm.com)
